"<p>The world of Zeronia is in perilous shape. As a member of a special, underground organization, you're tasked with defending the realm from the forces of darkness. You will traverse Zeronia, gathering weapons and supplies as you fight your way through the enemy's forces. As you progress, you will uncover the identity of the mastermind behind the plot and stop them from fulfilling their sinister goals. With each enemy you face, you will become stronger, collecting powerups to assist in your journey. The fate of Zeronia rests in your hands.</p>"